data.message: I believe #32 Wolves has a splinter in his eye. So maybe we're gonna go to eye doctor? The guy behind him looks to be waving for a doctor to come help him out
He's trying to remove the log from his eye so he can help get the speck off his neighbor's shirt.

message:
The Timberwolves game is TOMMOROW!!!

What you need to know:
Timeline: 
5:00 most all of us are getting on the light rail (That is when it LEAVES) 
5:30 Check in at Mayo Clinic Square front desk for a talk from Timberwolves team President (there will be time for questions) 
6:15 go over to target center 
6:30 high-five players before game 
7:00 Game

If you don’t know where Mayo Clinic Square is (1st Ave and 6th St), it is attached to the target center, look it up on Google maps, Mapquest, Yahoo maps, Bing maps whatever you wish, but you cannot be late! 

If you need any help text me or call me at 612-965-3956

Also I believe that you can still purchase a ticket if you haven’t already!  There are 84 people signed up!

I understand this is a lot of information but I have no way of getting it to you all except for this post so tell your friends!
